}}「[[培根|培根]]」（bacon）演變自[[古高地德語|古高地德語]]中的「bacho」（意為臀部、火腿或燻腹部肉），亦近於[[古法語|古法語]]中的「bacon」<ref>{{cite encyclopedia|title=Bacon|encyclopedia=OED Online|url=|volume=|pages=|publisher=[[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]|year=1989|id=50016435|accessdate=2009-03-15}}</ref>。培根由[[豬|豬]]的腹部肉（俗稱[[五花肉|五花肉]]）或背部肉製成，依切法不同而具有不等的脂肪含量<ref>{{cite web|title=The various cuts of bacon described|url=http://www.joyinfood.com/BaconCuts.html|publisher=Joy in Food|accessdate=2010-12-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100512162916/http://www.joyinfood.com/BaconCuts.html|archivedate=2010-05-12}}</ref>。它經醃製後，隨後以[[蘋果|蘋果木]]、[[牧豆|牧豆木]]、[[山胡桃|山胡桃木]]等木材煙燻<ref>{{cite web|title=Bacon - Ingredient|url=http://www.chow.com/ingredients/409|publisher=Chow|accessdate=2010-12-05|archive-date=2015-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207172949/http://www.chow.com/ingredients/409|dead-url=no}}</ref>。培根是烹飪時常見的食材或配料，各國菜肴中都可見到它的蹤影。

